headline: Interpublic Group (IPG) Drops After Competition Watchdog OK on Omnicom Merger
summary: We recently published These 10 Stocks Just Lost Their Spark. Interpublic Group of Companies Inc. (NYSE:IPG) is one of the worst-performing companies on Thursday. Interpublic saw its share prices drop by 4.25 percent on Thursday to end at $24.13 apiece following the Australian competition watchdog’s approval of its pending merger with Omnicom Group Inc.
